CheckBox example:

```js
<CheckBox
  label="Label-1"
  type="checkbox"
  name="label-1"
  value="checkbox-1"
  checked={state.checked}
  onChange={() => {
    /*Change checked status*/
    setState({ checked: !state.checked });
  }}
>
  <div>
    <span>Check first</span>
  </div>
</CheckBox>
```

